  "None suggested yet": "Nenhuma sugestão ainda",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Após a resposta, uma chamada silenciosa gera o JSON. ~250–300s/mensagem.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Uma chamada API — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Sem troca de perfil — sem risco",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ IA tem contexto completo",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× mais rápido que Separado",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Usa tokens do orçamento principal (~1.700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Pode reduzir ligeiramente a narrativa",
  "✓ Clean responses — narrative never token-competes with tracker": "✓ Respostas limpas — sem competição",
  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ Orçamento dedicado para o rastreador",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Pode usar perfil/preset diferente",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Duas chamadas API — 2–3× mais lento",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s de espera entre chamadas",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ com 8 msgs — reduza para 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Troca de perfil pode causar exclusão",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Incorpora snapshot anterior (~1.9K) a menos que = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Quantas mensagens recentes incluir ao atualizar.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Apenas modo Separado — Junto usa o contexto do ST.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Mais rápido. Para cenas 1 a 1 (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Equilibrado. Para a maioria (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Melhor continuidade para cenas complexas (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Máximo contexto mas mais lento e caro",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Maior fator de velocidade. Com 8 msgs ~10K — dobrar dobra o tempo. 3–4 reduz 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Apenas modo Separado.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Quantas vezes repetir se JSON inválido.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Para JSON no GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Incorpora snapshots no contexto narrativo. Apenas Separado. O rastreador sempre recebe o anterior.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Cada snapshot +~1.9K. 0 para eliminar. 1 para continuidade. Acima de 1 raramente útil.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Injetado como contexto invisível — tratado como info autoritativa.",
